        {
          "post_id": 2,
          "user_id": 1,
          "content": "Polymarket’s use of Polygon + USDC solved the fatal flaws of old prediction markets like Augur: high fees, poor UX, and complex tokens. This isn’t just an upgrade — it’s the first scalable, usable prediction market. The zero-fee model was genius for bootstrapping liquidity.",
          "num_likes": 5,
          "num_dislikes": 0
        },
        {
          "post_id": 1,
          "user_id": 0,
          "content": "Shayne Coplan built Polymarket in a bathroom during lockdown. Now it’s done $9B in volume, called the election early, and got a $2B investment from NYSE’s parent. From a 16-year-old ETH investor to a crypto maverick — this is the wild story of how prediction markets went mainstream. https://example.com/polymarket-rise",
          "num_likes": 1,
          "num_dislikes": 0
        },
        {
          "post_id": 3,
          "user_id": 2,
          "content": "Let’s not forget: Polymarket was fined $1.4M by the CFTC and raided by the FBI. This isn’t just a ‘disruptive startup’ story — it’s a regulatory time bomb. Just because it’s popular doesn’t mean it’s legal. The CFTC has been clear — these are derivatives, and they require oversight.",
          "num_likes": 0,
